Summary: Biochemical reaction from phenprocoumon to 7-hydroxyphenprocoumon. This interaction can be catalyzed by CYP2C9 or CYP3A4.
Biochemical reaction from phenprocoumon to 4'-hydroxyphenprocoumon. This interaction can be catalyzed by CYP2C8, CYP3A4 or CYP2C9.
Biochemical reaction from phenprocoumon to 6-hydroxyphenprocoumon. This interaction can be catalyzed by CYP3A4 or CYP2C9.
